Params: {3: 'You arrive in the frigid Port District...'}
{3: 'This place reminds you of Murmansk somehow...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sophia', 3: 'I dislike the cold, but Miss Celica requested my deployment.', 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: 'The intel says that the freight logistic system here is highly automated. Command assigned you Sophia just in case.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "And, just for your information, this is near Murmansk—you're in Kyaranta. Though, only the port is still intact.", 4: '2'}
{1: '2', 2: 'Celica', 3: "Babylonia decided to reactivate the purification filter here to accommodate some ARU refugees. When you're done here, you could even hitch a ride to Murmansk.", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "The facilities here look good as new. Doesn't look like the Corrupted have gotten their hands on it.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: 'When the Corrupted invaded this place, a high-frequency echo drew them all away.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: 'No clues as to the source of the echo, but the facilities survived because of that.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Not all of them were drawn away, it seems.', 4: '1'}
